=== fcutils ===

This is an eclectic collection of scripts.

=== Descriptions ===

  randmac    Generate a random MAC.
  randpass   Random password generator (depends on /dev/random).
  ssrc       I use this within the programming editor acme a lot to grep through source code. 
  cleantmp   Remove recovery files left behind by editors such as vi and emacs. 
  backup     A wrapper for rsync.
  fixmirror  Makes mirrors of websites downloaded with wget work.

=== Author(s) ===

Paco Pascal
